{"tid":2393190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"誤信洗衣機甩豆沙餡方便快捷　支那女子自製豆沙包照跟結果洗衣機爆炸","createTime":"2021-02-03T09:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T05:00:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":318,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"59907fd68cacf4329b627f90c4d77231e79deebe","tid":2393190,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:45:08.000Z","msg":"自製豆沙包竟使用洗衣機？黑龍江牡丹江市一名女子，聽信朋友所說，以為洗衣機甩豆沙餡方便快捷，自製豆沙包照跟，結果現場一片狼藉超崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n綜合内地媒體報道，一名女子將自己家中慘況拍下短片，稱想要自己製作豆沙包，從朋友那裡聽聞可以用洗衣機來攪豆沙餡，所以就使用洗衣機來做。<br />\n<br />\n結果洗衣機爆炸，將豆沙餡炸開，滿屋都是豆沙餡，而整台約700至800元人民幣的洗衣機也爆廢，女子無奈哀號「愁死我了！」<br />\n<br />\n短片爆光後引起網民熱議，大批網民揶揄該名女子是沒常識，「人才啊，洗衣機攪豆沙」、「這豆沙包成本太高了」、「洗衣機很髒的，就算沒爆炸炸，能吃嗎？」、「應該是豆沙在一坨了，然後轉筒把洗衣機撞壞了」、「腦子真是個好東西」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869907/redbean_thumb_20210203_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869907%2Fredbean_thumb_20210203_S_1024.jpg&h=fe58cbab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869907/2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869907%2F2_1024.jpg&h=75759a06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869907/3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869907%2F3_1024.jpg&h=a8e34383&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d1b6c7e566b57bd7b76bcbba9a7ee22052a71ab","tid":2393190,"uid":35430,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:45:57.000Z","msg":"係咪咁聰明？"},{"pid":"117ee4d3c586a42949d8c093049538fd068236c7","tid":2393190,"uid":39826,"like":402,"dislike":1,"score":401,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩你玩屎"},{"pid":"10340f7d4fe1111484e21e06fc9221b648369356","t